caption: "Electronic nicotine delivery system"
created: 20260405120000000
modified: 20260405120000000
title: Policy1331(s1)(4)
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

shall mean an electronic device used in the delivery of nicotine to a person inhaling from the device and includes, but is not limited to, an electronic cigarette, electronic cigar, electronic cigarillo, electronic pipe or electronic hookah and any related device and any cartridge or other component of such device, including, but not limited to, electronic cigarette liquid or synthetic nicotine.
